Interface LoggingValidatorInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NewsAPILoggingValidator
    public interface LoggingValidatorInterface
    Represents service facilitating testable determining if logs of particular level should be added. Logging exceptions shouldn't be validated.
